divs: Sighting DetailsI was at a park with some friends just hanging out. I noticed something in the sky moving, thought it was geese at first. As I continued to watch I realized the object had a shape to it, and what i thought, for a split second, were geese flying in formation, were actually dim circular lights on the underbelly of a boomerang shaped object . I watched the object fly in a straight line for about 5 seconds, then it completely disappeared. Thought I was crazy for a little bit, but I couldn't deny what I saw. I didn't tell my friends at first, because I didn't think they'd take me seriously. Decided to report what I saw when I read an article about someone who had seen exactly what I did.
